text: Jay Shree Krishna , our Parents from African countries at some stage of their lives surrendered Indian Nationality and become British Subjects . When I applied for OCI Overseas Citizen Of India with my British Passport and Uganda born Birth Certificate the application was turned down saying that they required an Indian Document saying that either one of my Parents or I are Indian Born and my parents British passports stating that they were Indian Born were not acceptable . My father wrote to Delhi Indian Home Office to send either proof or his original Passport he surrendered 3 years ago but have not received any reply . What is annoying is most of the community leaders know of the difficulty but despite attending meetings and function with Indian High Commissioner and the staff none have raised the issue that it is very unfair to discard completely a British Passport stating that the person is born in India . Furthermore , why is it impossible receive either surrendered passport or proof that my father was an Indian Citizen before becoming British Citizen . Please share if you have faced this problem .

text: #295 : This is an Inter-IIT love story . I was a simple guy and never ever thought I will fall in love or get addicted to a girl . As it happens , a girl came in my life and she changed me completely . I was totally infatuated with her and watched as everything around me including my personality changed just for her . I was obsessing about her nonstop ... wanted to be there with her , for her ... everywhere , everytime . I wanted to be her first , last and only point of contact . In time she got into another IIT . But then she started meeting other people and avoiding me , and it made me feel very disturbed . Then she dropped the ultimate cock-blocking man-bomb and said that she doesn't want this relationship and I agreed to friendzoned ( yes i cock-blocked myself ) . Man this killed me and affected everything around me , felt like the world had caved in suddenly . Obviously it affected my endsems also . I am able to accept if she gets a boyfriend but I can't imagine them having sex , it totally kills me . I really need to talk to her and be around her . I have learned the hard way to live without her but being with her adds great happiness to my life ... come back if you don't have a boyfriend .
